e Launch Rocket System|GMLRS]] Multiple Launch Rocket Systems, to be divisional fires regiment<ref name=\":1\" /><ref name=\"mead\">{{cite web|url=https://3.bp.blogspot.com/-xEUsn7hxDMo/WFMZfObk8EI/AAAAAAAAEho/2hLXO0xUOVUYorc22jED3FsIzvghnhEVgCLcB/s1600/Czv9xzCWIAE-W1B.jpg|title=Letter from Brigadier Mead|publisher=1st Artillery Brigade and Headquarters South West|accessdate=16 December 2016}}</ref><ref name=\"mead2\">{{cite web|url=https://scontent.xx.fbcdn.net/v/t1.0-9/15492571_1338253552859669_4065325510072663045_n.jpg?oh=aec9617d2b8b8b163d0421a7f28ed84b&oe=58F15783 |title=Letter from Brigadier Mead Part 2 |publisher=1st Artillery Brigade and Headquarters South West |accessdate=19 December 2016 }}{{dead link|date=June 2017 |bot=InternetArchiveBot |fix-attempted=yes }}</ref>\n*** [[101 (Northumbrian) Regiment Royal Artillery]], in [[Gateshead]] <ref name=\"mead\">{{cite web|url=https://3.bp.blogspot.com/-xEUsn7hxDMo/WFMZfObk8EI/AAAAAAAAEho/2hLXO0xUOVUYorc22jED3FsIzvghnhEVgCLcB/s1600/Czv9xzCWIAE-W1B.jpg|title=Letter from Brigadier Mead|publisher=1st Artillery Brigade and Headquarters South West|accessdate=16 December 2016}}</ref><ref name=\"mead2\">{{cite web|url=https://scontent.xx.fbcdn.net/v/t1.0-9/15492571_1338253552859669_4065325510072663045_n.jpg?oh=aec9617d2b8b8b163d0421a7f28ed84b&oe=58F15783 |title=Letter from Brigadier Mead Part 2 |publisher=1st Artillery Brigade and Headquarters South West |accessdate=19 December 2016 }}{{dead link|date=June 2017 |bot=InternetArchiveBot |fix-attempted=yes }}</ref>\n\n==== 101 Logistic Brigade ====\n* '''[[101st Logistic Brigade (United Kingdom)|101 Logistic Brigade]]''', in Aldershot\n** [[156 Regiment RLC|156 Regiment]] [[Royal Logistic Corps]], in [[Liverpool]] (Army Reserve supply regiment)\n** 1 Regiment Royal Military Police (1 RMP) in [[Catterick Garrison|Catterick]]<ref name=ZacchiFOI />\n** 3 Regiment Royal Military Police (3 RMP) in [[Bulford Camp|Bulford]]<ref name=ZacchiFOI />\n** 160 Provost Company, supportin