{"title_page": "A Time to Heal (film)", "text_new": "{{refimprove|date=April 2016}}\n{{Infobox television\n| show_name      = A Time to Heal\n| image          =\n| caption        =\n| genre          = Drama \n| director       = [[Michael Toshiyuki Uno]]\n| executive_producer = \n| producer       = [[Susan Baerwald]]<br>[[Lewis Abel]] (co-producer)\n| writer         = [[Cathleen Young]]\n| starring       = [[Nicollette Sheridan]]<br>[[Gary Cole]]<br>[[Mara Wilson]]\n| cinematography = [[Newton Thomas Sigel]]\n| editor         = [[David A. Simmons]]\n| theme_music_composer = [[Jay Gruska]]\n| company        = [[NBC Productions]]<br>[[Susan Baerwald Productions]]\n| distributor    = [[National Broadcasting Company|NBC]]\n| network        = NBC\n| released       = April 18, 1994\n| runtime        = 90 minutes\n| language       = English\n| country        = [[United States]]\n}}\n\n'''''A Time to Heal''''' is a 1994 [[TV movie]] starring [[Nicollette Sheridan]], [[Gary Cole]] and [[Mara Wilson]].<ref name=\"A Time to Heal\">{{cite web|url=http://www.tcm.com/tcmdb/title/479616/Time-to-Heal-A/full-credits.html|accessdate=April 23, 2016|work=[[Turner Classic Movies]]|title=A Time to Heal}}</ref> The TV film was directed by [[Michael Toshiyuki Uno]].<ref name=\"A Time to Heal\"/>\n\n==Plot==\nA mother that has been paralyzed from a stroke during [[childbirth]] recovers with the help of her husband.\n\n==Cast==\n* [[Nicollette Sheridan]] as Jenny Barton\n* [[Gary Cole]] as Jay Barton\n* [[Mara Wilson]] as Barbara Barton\n* [[Annie Corley]] as Michelle Rogers\n* [[Ken Jenkins]] as Don Peterson\n* [[Ben Masters]] as Dr. Klein\n* [[Tim Ransom]] as Mitch Barton\n* [[Lorraine Toussaint]] as Zelda\n* [[Doris Roberts]] as Maddy\n* [[Bryan Clark]] as Mr. Barton\n* [[Toni Sawyer]] as Mrs. Barton\n* [[Scott Alan Smith]] as Dr. Martin\n* [[Trisha Simmons]] as Nurse Johnson\n* [[Wesley Hayashi]] as Burt\n* [[Sarah Freeman (actress)|Sarah Freeman]] as Sandra\n* [[Lauren Kopit]] as Beth\n\